# OS
Operating system used is Windows. Only use terminal commands etc., that are compatible with Windows.

# JS runtime
The project uses Bun as its package manager and JavaScript runtime, not NPM.

# No TypeScript
The project does NOT use TypeScript, opting for JavaScript instead. This is extremely important!

# Svelte 5
The project uses Svelte 5 in runes mode. Keep that in mind at all times as certain Svelte 4 code and approaches are incompatible with Svelte 5.


